rows.label: qst104707_msg001
rows.name: 大変だ 助けよう(仮)

rows.label: qst104707_msg0001
rows.name: Everyone, please calm down-

rows.label: qst104707_msg0002
rows.name:
This is way more people than
you led on you were going to
be! What are you playin' at?

rows.label: qst104707_msg0003
rows.name:
There was a sudden influx of
people wanting to board the
ship just before it departed...

rows.label: qst104707_msg0004
rows.name: Don't go making out it was our fault!

rows.label: qst104707_msg0005
rows.name:
Did you or did you not tell us
that Torigo would be able to
handle a few extra people?

rows.label: qst104707_msg0006
rows.name:
Well, I mean, I... I just
knew that the people from
Torigo were kind, so...

rows.label: qst104707_msg0007
rows.name:
You're one of them who went and
got themselves scouted, is it?

rows.label: qst104707_msg0008
rows.name:
This town not good enough for you,
eh? Had to go to the capital and be
a good little slave for the bigwigs?

rows.label: qst104707_msg0009
rows.name:
You know the trouble Superbia's
put us through, but you still
go lapping at their boots.

rows.label: qst104707_msg0010
rows.name:
The cost of food's going to go right
up. We're all going to starve.

rows.label: qst104707_msg0011
rows.name: I don't think-

rows.label: qst104707_msg0012
rows.name:
Berating your countryman like that?
Just what I'd expect from Gulan.

rows.label: qst104707_msg0013
rows.name:
If you've got something to say to
me, boyo, you can say it straight!

rows.label: qst104707_msg0014
rows.name:
Doriath, these arseholes
can live on our Divine
Beast over my dead body!

rows.label: qst104707_msg0015
rows.name: P-please just calm down...

rows.label: qst104707_msg0016
rows.name: Just whose side are you on anyway?

rows.label: qst104707_msg0017
rows.name:
Oh, um, well... Look, just
stop fighting, please!

rows.label: qst104707_msg0018
rows.name:
And who's fault is it that
we're fighting, by you?

rows.label: qst104707_msg0019
rows.name:
You've really made a pig's ear of
this intermediary business, boy.

rows.label: qst104707_msg0020
rows.name:
Forgive my intrusion but
Orca is not at fault here.

rows.label: qst104707_msg0021
rows.name:
An animal Blade? Did you really need
to resonate with this piece of rubbish
just to pretend you're an Superbian?

rows.label: qst104707_msg0022
rows.name: How could you-

rows.label: qst104707_msg0023
rows.name: I can't let that slide.

rows.label: qst104707_msg0024
rows.name: Byakko!

rows.label: qst104707_msg0025
rows.name:
An insult to our friends
is an insult to us.

rows.label: qst104707_msg0026
rows.name:
I had thought that if it looked
like people were going to get
hurt, I would step in and help.

rows.label: qst104707_msg0027
rows.name:
But your words have even
my calm blood boiling.

rows.label: qst104707_msg0028
rows.name:
Maybe my water powers will
help you cool off a little!
